#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. I"
msgid_plural "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. Is"
msgstr[0] "仿生空间扩展器 CBM Mk. I"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. I'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander Mk. I'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Nanobots replace large parts of the involuntary muscles with an innovativ, "
"synthetic muscle structure (that's far smaller but equally capable) to "
"expand the available space for bionic implementations."
msgstr "纳米机器人将大部分不随意肌替换为创新的合成肌肉结构（体积更小但功能相当），以扩大可用于仿生植入的空间。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. II"
msgid_plural "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. IIs"
msgstr[0] "仿生空间扩展器 CBM Mk. II"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. II'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander Mk. II'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Parts of the stroma and skeleton get replaced by nanobots with small storage"
" units to significantly increase the space for bionic implementations in all"
" bodyparts."
msgstr "纳米机器人替换部分基质与骨骼，并配备小型存储单元，显著增加全身各部位可用于仿生植入的空间。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. III"
msgid_plural "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. IIIs"
msgstr[0] "仿生空间扩展器 CBM Mk. III"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. III'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander Mk. III'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Within picoseconds mikro teleport systems cut currently unused bionic "
"implants in an uncountable number of pieces, move them to otherwise unusable"
" space (like the fat tissue) and restore now needed implants on that "
"location."
msgstr "微秒级微传送系统将当前未使用的仿生植入体切割成无数碎片，移至原本无法利用的空间（如脂肪组织），并在该位置恢复当前所需的植入体。"

#: .\bionics.json
msgid "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. IV"
msgid_plural "Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. IVs"
msgstr[0] "仿生空间扩展器 CBM Mk. IV"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander CBM Mk. IV'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bionic Space Expander Mk. IV'}
#: .\bionics.json
msgid ""
"Through quantum tunneling most of your implants aren't in this universe "
"anymore ... wherever they are: you've got a lot more space for bionic "
"implementations!"
msgstr "通过量子隧穿效应，你的大部分植入体已不在此宇宙中……无论它们身处何方：你获得了更多仿生植入空间！"

